 maxAge: 86400
How long (in seconds) the browser should cache the preflight OPTIONS response.

86400 = 24 hours
So the browser doesn’t keep spamming OPTIONS requests over and over again.

optionsSuccessStatus: 204
Preflight requests (OPTIONS) respond with status 204 instead of 200.

💡 Some old browsers (like IE 😖) hang if the status isn’t 204.
















